  <id>io.github.sameboy.SameBoy</id>
  <name>SameBoy</name>
  <summary>Game Boy and Game Boy Color emulator</summary>
  <developer_name>Lior Halphon</developer_name>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  <description>
    <p>SameBoy is an open source Game Boy (DMG) and Game Boy Color (CGB) emulator,
written in portable C. It has an SDL frontend and a libretro core.
It also includes a text-based debugger with an expression evaluator.</p>
  </description>
